{/* Content */}
{/* Welcome Section */}

Welcome to SnapVault

The Ultimate Secure Photo Gallery Platform

SnapVault is not just another cloud photo storage. It’s a next-generation platform designed to protect your digital memories with military-grade encryption, intelligent organization, and seamless sharing—all under your control.

We combine intuitive design with advanced cybersecurity to deliver a gallery experience that’s as safe as it is simple.

{/* What Makes SnapVault Unique */}

🔍 What Makes SnapVault Unique?

End-to-End Security

Your photos are encrypted on your device before they ever reach our servers. Only you—and those you explicitly authorize—can access your content. We use AES-256 and TLS 1.3 to keep data secure at all times.

Smart Photo Management

Auto-categorization by date, location, faces, and events—without compromising your privacy. Search your gallery with powerful filters, not AI models trained on your content.

Private Sharing, Redefined

Share albums securely with expiring links, password-protection, and view/download tracking. Revoke access at any time.

Cloud Convenience & Local Options

Access your gallery from any device. Choose to store backups on your device, private cloud, or encrypted drives.

No Ads. No Tracking. Ever.

We are privacy-first, not ad-driven. No facial recognition sent to third parties. No hidden analytics. Just full transparency.

Secure Payments

All payments are processed through PCI DSS-compliant gateways with end-to-end encryption. Your billing details are never stored unencrypted, ensuring total peace of mind.
{/* Who Is SnapVault For? */}

Who Is SnapVault For?

  • Families & Everyday Users
    Preserve and protect your memories across generations.
  • Professional Photographers
    Deliver secure client albums with watermarking and download control.
  • Enterprises & Agencies
    Manage sensitive media with granular permissions, audit logs, and access control.
{/* How to Get Started */}

How to Get Started

  1. Create Your Free Account
    Get started in seconds with just an email. No credit card required.
  2. Upload & Organize
    Import photos from your device, Google Photos, Dropbox, or directly via drag-and-drop.
  3. Secure & Share
    Create albums, apply security controls, and share with peace of mind.
{/* Privacy Commitment */}

Your Privacy Is Our Priority

We’re committed to digital freedom. With SnapVault:

  • You own your photos.
  • You control who sees them.
  • You decide how long they stay.
  • No third parties. No fine print. No compromises.

{/* Device Availability */}

Available on All Devices

  • iOS & Android Apps
  • Web-based Dashboard
  • Desktop Upload Tool (Windows/Mac/Linux)

— Aditi M., Mom & Engineer
“Client delivery used to be a nightmare. Now it’s secure and seamless.”
— Ravi S., Wedding Photographer
